<function>

access:   public

name: style

param: string, $href

param: array, $attribs, NULL

return: string

</function>

Returns a <style>...</style> tag.

* Parameters:

 * string //$href//: The source href for the stylesheet.

 * array //$attribs//: Additional attributes for the <style> tag.

* Returns string: The <style>...</style> tag.

Returns a <style>...</style> tag.

Adds "media" attribute if not specified, and always uses
"type" attribute of "text/css".